.planning/knowledge/signals/get-shit-done-reflect/2026-03-02-reflect-to-spike-pipeline-untested-end-to-end.md:46:The reflect-to-spike pipeline -- the path from a reflection report identifying a Genuine Gap through to spike creation -- has never been exercised with real data. No persistent reflection reports exist under `~/.gsd/knowledge/reflections/`. All pipeline verification was performed via static code inspection rather than end-to-end empirical testing.
