.planning/knowledge/signals/get-shit-done-reflect/sig-2026-03-05-phase40-plan-gaps-pre-execution-review.md:40:Plan 02 hardcodes context estimate as 40. The deferral threshold is 60%. Since 40 < 60 always, context deferral never triggers. SIG-05 is syntactically satisfied but functionally dead.
.planning/knowledge/signals/get-shit-done-reflect/sig-2026-03-05-phase40-plan-gaps-pre-execution-review.md:43:Plan 01 adds lock/unlock/check-lock/regime-change commands with manual verification only. Every prior phase that added gsd-tools.js commands also added automated tests (Phase 37: automation.test.js, Phase 38: sensors tests). This breaks the project's testing convention.
