.planning/knowledge/signals/get-shit-done-reflect/2026-02-22-plan-22-03-incomplete-interrupted.md:41:Most likely a context window interruption or agent timeout during the 22-03 execution. The wave-parallel execution of Plans 02/03/04 (all running within seconds of each other based on commit timestamps) may have caused resource contention. The lack of a SUMMARY.md at completion time is a strong indicator the executor was interrupted before it could finalize. The delayed SUMMARY (3 days later) was created by a different session with reconstructed knowledge.
