    59	**Notes:** Five philosophical principles grounded in Goodhart, Kuhn/Hanson, Mayo, Hacking, and a meta-principle of metric reflexivity. These are not decorative — they constrain design decisions (e.g., metrics as indicators not targets, epistemic humility convention for every metric output).
